# Audit Methodology Changelog

All notable changes to the audit methodology of this project. Format: [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/).

Versioning is semantic at the methodology level:
- **MAJOR** — incompatible changes (renamed IDs, removed statuses)
- **MINOR** — new check added, new audit type added
- **PATCH** — clarifications, typo fixes

