## [1.0.0] — {{DATE}}

### Added

- Initial methodology based on AIDEX audit-conventions.
- Six core principles (Finding ≠ Issue ≠ Task; INVENTORY as SoT; living methodology; findings never deleted; escalation flow; shared concerns flagged).
- Status lifecycle: open → triaged → escalated → in-progress → closed / dropped.
- Severity levels: P0 / P1 / P2 / P3.

